g.text: Mark exact copies as duplicates w/ Attribute: "C"
FIND ROWS DUPLICATE OF REFERENCE ROWS (HIGH CONFIDENCE)
CRITERIA: >80% Name and then >40% Address Similarity
FIND REMAINING DUPLICATES ESCAPED FROM 1st Phase (HIGH CONFIDENCE)
CRITERIA for Duplicates: 100% Name and then >90% Address Similarity
CRITERIA for Highly Similar: 70-100% Name and then 70-90% Address Similarity
Mark higly similar ones w/ Attribute: "HS"
